{"tid":2238535,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港大研究生選校委 冀破內地生壟斷","createTime":"2020-10-11T08:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T09:19:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7441060227cc445bf505dadda1c018f3215468dd","tid":2238535,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T08:02:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201011/NQJLKOPL2NDTFCVQLFZFZ7ORNQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201011%2FNQJLKOPL2NDTFCVQLFZFZ7ORNQ%2F&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUleCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=8ecfbdf7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201011%2FNQJLKOPL2NDTFCVQLFZFZ7ORNQ%2F&h=31198a77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201011/NQJLKOPL2NDTFCVQLFZFZ7ORNQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港大研究生選校委 冀破內地生壟斷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ken3M7sIIbQx3h6SjzjCOELgOdw=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TRCMZ7EKIJHWDKKQGM65WUHHKA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fken3M7sIIbQx3h6SjzjCOELgOdw%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTRCMZ7EKIJHWDKKQGM65WUHHKA.jpg&h=aa5b4370&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■葉子健日前在連儂牆受訪，指希望參選喚起港大人對校政關注。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】7月投票通過解僱佔中發起人、法律學系副教授戴耀廷的港大校務委員會，研究生代表一席明日起一連三日舉行換屆選舉。今年由港大一年級研究生葉子健與研究生會現任主席、內地生張潤智競逐。該席多年來由內地生把持，葉承認作為香港學生勝算不大，但仍希望參選喚起港大人對校政的關注。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現屆代表贊成炒戴耀廷<br />\n<br />\n現時校委會23名委員中僅七人為民選代表，包括本科生及研究生代表各一以及五名教職員代表。據了解，今年7月來自內地的現屆研究生代表王宇辰為「炒戴」投下贊成票。就讀文學及文化研究碩士課程一年級的葉子健稱，校委會研究生代表一席多年來由內地生出任，投票前不會諮詢同學意見，甚至在「炒戴」會議中作出與學生主流意見相反的決定。即使他當選也僅有一票，無力扭轉局面，但仍希望透過以港人身份出選，喚醒同學對校政的關注。<br />\n<br />\n葉批評對手作為港大研究生會主席，只專注服務內地生：「無論係福利、發佈資訊都係用微信。」早前在facebook形容自己「贏面唔大」的他稱只要香港學生團結，「相信會有奇迹」。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n校委會為港大最高管治機關，根據條例可行使大學所有權力，包括解散或改革研究所、專科學院，甚至終止校長聘任。本報曾邀約張潤智訪問，張以事務繁忙為由婉拒。"},{"pid":"54c2d4d93550469f5f69a44334e0fc9391bd60dd","tid":2238535,"uid":205772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T08:14:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60993ce0fe88d99b441fe63a149f64d73d8749c1","tid":2238535,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T08:34:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64abede53490e0c9e367e82f24b3695ce70fa3b","tid":2238535,"uid":112185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T07:01:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"34fe0d0f02bf18acf3764ec7c2ebf8120f5813e2","tid":2238535,"uid":112185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T07:05:13.000Z","msg":"港大校委會及教委會研究生代表選舉周三結束 香港代表葉子健朱顥廷對撼陸生張潤智王宇辰：至少1200票才穩勝<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2240099\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2240099</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6ef3aeb9231a3c4c471d88697108455f211ad1e4","tid":2238535,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34fe0d0f02bf18acf3764ec7c2ebf8120f5813e2","tid":2238535,"uid":112185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T07:05:13.000Z","msg":"港大校委會及教委會研究生代表選舉周三結束 香港代表葉子健朱顥廷對撼陸生張潤智王宇辰：至少1200票才穩勝<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2240099\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2240099</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T07:07:06.000Z","msg":"Pinned"},{"pid":"01d6c24f07fd5ef886b4c6f18665ed3ab2402c12","tid":2238535,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T07:07:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727ef834da11f1b2c3ba36b888ee641b1add